<img src="http://newsroom.uts.edu.au/sites/default/files/styles/wide_landscape/public/images/article_feature/file-20180302-65529-qqrksd.jpg?itok=Mv69yg6D" width="980" height="490" alt="Blood has always been a symbol of life and has been thought to counteract the ageing process. Mai Lam/The Conversation NY-BD-CC, CC BY-SA" title="Blood has always been a symbol of life and has been thought to counteract the ageing process. Mai Lam/The Conversation NY-BD-CC, CC BY-SA" /></div>
