              <div class="slide__constrained">        <div class="slide__caption">
          
                      
                          <h2 class="slide__title">Winning team members (back row, from the left) But Wing Yin, Mohammad Al-Qazwini, Harris Jabbour, Keisha Prasad and Yeshi Tsomo. Front row, finalists Amolika Dhugana and Katarina Gomola. Picture by H. Chen</h2>
            
            
            
            
